sources.description:
When solar debris rains down upon Earth, it sparks catastrophic destruction across the planet. The fallout from this impact releases intense solar radiation, mutating anyone who comes into contact with it. As the radiation spreads uncontrollably, chaos ensues, throwing governments and military forces worldwide into disarray and collapse. Amidst the unraveling of society, a small group of unlikely companions bands together, fighting to survive in a world that no longer resembles the one they once knew. With their lives at risk and no clear refuge in sight, they must navigate a brutal landscape of mutated horrors and societal ruin, desperately searching for safety before itâ€™s too late.
